sub_title: Policy Intern at the Embassy of the Kingdom of the Netherlands in Albania | MA European Policy at the University of Amsterdam | Humaned Foundation
summary:
Master Student of European Policy at the University of Amsterdam. My specialisations encompass EU Politics and the Common Foreign and Security Policy of the EU. 

Currently, I am also pursuing an internship as a Policy Intern at the Embassy of the Netherlands in Tirana, Albania.

I am interested in Politics, International Relations, European co-operation, Climate Change, Sustainability, Infrastructure and Humanitarian Aid. I like researching, writing and debating. In my spare time I like to meet people, practice language skills, read, cook and travel.
